<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>PEPPOL France · Comptages quotidiens · {{ production_date_short }}</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@100..900&family=Geist+Mono:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --peppol-red-dark:    #C00404;
  --peppol-red:         #D90D25;
  --peppol-black:       #181818;
  --peppol-gray-light:  #F3F3F6;
  --peppol-r800:        #660000;
  --peppol-r700:        #960000;
  --peppol-r400:        #FF6464;
  --peppol-r300:        #FF9696;
  --peppol-r200:        #FFC8C8;
  --peppol-r100:        #FFF0F0;
  --peppol-white:       #FFFFFF;

  --bg:           var(--peppol-white);
  --text:         var(--peppol-black);
  --text-muted:   var(--peppol-r800);
  --title:        var(--peppol-red-dark);
  --accent:       var(--peppol-red);
  --card:         var(--peppol-r100);
  --border:       var(--peppol-r200);

  --font-sans: "Geist", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-mono: "Geist Mono", "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
}

@page {
  size: A4;
  margin: 18mm 14mm 22mm 14mm;

  @bottom-left {
    content: "Comptages quotidiens · PEPPOL France · adoption EXTENDED-CTC-FR";
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #660000;
    padding-top: 5mm;
    border-top: 0.5pt solid #FFC8C8;
    width: 150mm;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  @bottom-right {
    content: "Page " counter(page) " / " counter(pages);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #C00404;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding-top: 5mm;
    border-top: 0.5pt solid #FFC8C8;
    width: 25mm;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-align: right;
    vertical-align: top;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  @top-right {
    content: "{{ author_short }} · {{ production_date_short }}";
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #660000;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
}

@page :first {
  margin-top: 14mm;
  @top-right { content: ""; }
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 10.5pt;
  line-height: 1.55;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

.frame {
  max-width: 1240px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 56px 96px;
}

@media print {
  .frame { padding: 0; }
}

/* ─── MASTHEAD ───────────────────────────────── */
.masthead {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
  padding: 20px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--peppol-r200);
}

.peppol-block {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: var(--peppol-red);
  color: var(--peppol-white);
  padding: 8px 14px;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.masthead .meta {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.masthead .right {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-align: right;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

/* ─── HERO ───────────────────────────────────── */
.hero { padding: 36px 0 24px; }

.hero .label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11pt;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 32pt;
  line-height: 1.0;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: var(--text);
}

.subtitle {
  margin-top: 16px;
  font-size: 12pt;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.subtitle strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

/* ─── SECTION ────────────────────────────────── */
section {
  margin-top: 40px;
  page-break-inside: avoid;
}

h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18pt;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  line-height: 1.15;
}
h2 .sub {
  display: inline;
  margin-left: 14px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10pt;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-weight: 400;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

/* ─── TABLE ──────────────────────────────────── */
.t {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 10.5pt;
}
.t thead th {
  background: var(--peppol-red);
  color: var(--peppol-white);
  text-align: left;
  padding: 9px 12px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9pt;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.t thead th.num { text-align: right; }
.t tbody td {
  padding: 9px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  vertical-align: top;
}
.t tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--card); }
.t tbody td.num {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  text-align: right;
  font-feature-settings: "tnum" 1;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.t .label-cell {
  font-weight: 500;
}
.t .label-cell small {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8.5pt;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.t .ext { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
.t .pos { color: var(--peppol-r800); }
.t .neg { color: var(--text-muted); }
.t .zero { color: var(--text-muted); }
.t .dash { color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

/* ─── CHARTS ─────────────────────────────────── */
.charts {
  display: grid;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}
.chart-panel {
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 18px 20px;
}
.chart-panel .chart-title {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10pt;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.chart-panel svg {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

/* ─── METHOD ─────────────────────────────────── */
.method {
  background: var(--peppol-black);
  color: var(--peppol-white);
  padding: 22px 26px;
  margin-top: 36px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9pt;
  line-height: 1.55;
  page-break-inside: avoid;
}
.method h2 {
  color: var(--peppol-white);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9pt;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.method h2::before {
  content: "";
  display: block;
  width: 20px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--peppol-red);
}
.method p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.method code {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  padding: 1px 5px;
  font-size: 8.5pt;
  color: var(--peppol-r300);
}
.method a {
  color: var(--peppol-r300);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--peppol-red);
}

/* ─── COLOPHON ───────────────────────────────── */
.colophon {
  margin-top: 32px;
  padding-top: 18px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9pt;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.colophon .right { text-align: right; }
.colophon a {
  color: var(--text);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
}
.colophon .brand {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.colophon .brand .peppol-mini {
  background: var(--peppol-red);
  color: var(--peppol-white);
  padding: 3px 7px;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="frame">

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="peppol-block">@Sandjab</div>
  <div class="meta">Comptages quotidiens · PEPPOL France</div>
  <div class="right">Publié le {{ production_date_short }}</div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="label">Snapshot Peppol Directory · country=FR</div>
  <h1>Adoption EXTENDED-CTC-FR — comptages au {{ production_date_short }}.</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    Historique sur <strong>{{ num_runs }}</strong> jour{% if num_runs > 1 %}s{% endif %}
    {%- if date_range_start != date_range_end %}, du <strong>{{ date_range_start_short }}</strong> au <strong>{{ date_range_end_short }}</strong>{% endif %}.
    Source&nbsp;: <code style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9pt;background:var(--card);padding:1px 5px;">directory.peppol.eu/search/1.0/json</code>.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ─── SECTION : COMPTAGES BRUTS ─── -->
<section>
  <h2>Comptages bruts du jour <span class="sub">country=FR</span></h2>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Doctype</th>
        <th class="num">Participants FR</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
{%- for row in counts_rows %}
      <tr>
        <td class="label-cell">{% if row.ext %}<span class="ext">{{ row.label }}</span>{% else %}{{ row.label }}{% endif %}<small>{{ row.urn_short }}</small></td>
        <td class="num">{{ row.value|fr_int }}</td>
      </tr>
{%- endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ─── SECTION : ÉVOLUTION ─── -->
{%- if has_history %}
<section>
  <h2>Évolution <span class="sub">deltas vs J−1 · J−7 · origine</span></h2>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Doctype</th>
        <th class="num">Aujourd'hui</th>
        <th class="num">Δ J−1</th>
        <th class="num">Δ J−7</th>
        <th class="num">Δ origine</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
{%- for row in evolution_rows %}
      <tr>
        <td class="label-cell">{% if row.ext %}<span class="ext">{{ row.label }}</span>{% else %}{{ row.label }}{% endif %}</td>
        <td class="num">{{ row.value|fr_int }}</td>
        <td class="num {{ row.d1_class }}">{{ row.d1 }}</td>
        <td class="num {{ row.d7_class }}">{{ row.d7 }}</td>
        <td class="num {{ row.d_orig_class }}">{{ row.d_orig }}</td>
      </tr>
{%- endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:9pt;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.55;">
    Références effectives&nbsp;:
    Δ J−1 = vs <strong>{{ evolution_refs.j1.date_short }}</strong>{% if evolution_refs.j1.date and evolution_refs.j1.drift %} <span style="color:var(--accent)">(écart réel&nbsp;: {{ evolution_refs.j1.gap_days }}&nbsp;j)</span>{% elif evolution_refs.j1.gap_days %} ({{ evolution_refs.j1.gap_days }}&nbsp;j){% endif %} ·
    Δ J−7 = vs <strong>{{ evolution_refs.j7.date_short }}</strong>{% if evolution_refs.j7.date and evolution_refs.j7.drift %} <span style="color:var(--accent)">(écart réel&nbsp;: {{ evolution_refs.j7.gap_days }}&nbsp;j)</span>{% elif evolution_refs.j7.gap_days %} ({{ evolution_refs.j7.gap_days }}&nbsp;j){% endif %} ·
    Δ origine = vs <strong>{{ evolution_refs.orig.date_short }}</strong>{% if evolution_refs.orig.gap_days %} ({{ evolution_refs.orig.gap_days }}&nbsp;j){% endif %}.
    {% if evolution_refs.j1.drift or evolution_refs.j7.drift %}En rouge&nbsp;: la fenêtre nominale n'est pas respectée à cause d'un trou dans l'historique.{% endif %}
    « — » = pas d'historique disponible à ce pas.
  </p>
</section>
{%- endif %}

<!-- ─── SECTION : GRAPHIQUES ─── -->
{%- if has_history %}
<section>
  <h2>Évolution graphique</h2>
  <div class="charts">
    <div class="chart-panel">
      <div class="chart-title">Volumes par doctype (FR)</div>
      {{ svg_volumes | safe }}
    </div>
    <div class="chart-panel">
      <div class="chart-title">Taux d'adoption EXTENDED-CTC-FR (UBL Invoice EXT ÷ UBL Invoice CIUS)</div>
      {{ svg_ratio | safe }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{%- endif %}

<!-- ─── MÉTHODE ─── -->
<section class="method">
  <h2>Méthode &amp; reproductibilité</h2>
  <p>Données extraites de l'API publique <strong>Peppol Directory</strong> (OpenPeppol AISBL) via <code>/search/1.0/json?country=FR&amp;rpc=1</code> pour chacun des 6 doctypes France listés. Snapshot daté du <strong>{{ production_datetime_long }}</strong>.</p>
  <p>Le chiffre par doctype provient du champ <code>total-result-count</code> renvoyé par l'API (comptage exhaustif côté serveur sur l'index Directory). L'historique est conservé dans <code>peppol_history.json</code>, une entrée par jour, écrasement si re-run. Indexation Directory asynchrone&nbsp;: variations de quelques pour-cent jour à jour possibles, indépendantes des déclarations SMP réelles.</p>
  <p>Référence PASR&nbsp;: <a href="{{ pasr_url }}" target="_blank">France PASR 2026.02.27</a> (§6 et §7 — formats de réception obligatoires pour les PA).</p>
</section>

<footer class="colophon">
  <div>
    <div class="brand"><span class="peppol-mini">@Sandjab</span> Comptages quotidiens · PEPPOL France</div>
    Rapport produit par <strong style="color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">{{ author_full }}</strong><br>
    Date de production&nbsp;: {{ production_date_short }}<br>
    Données &copy; OpenPeppol AISBL — <a href="https://directory.peppol.eu" target="_blank">directory.peppol.eu</a>
  </div>
  <div class="right">
    PASR PEPPOL France 27 fév. 2026<br>
    <a href="{{ pasr_url }}" target="_blank">openpeppol.atlassian.net</a>
  </div>
</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
